title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 10 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 10 2021
description:
More real-time analysis of the Rittenhouse case, as Clay puts on his lawyer hat to break it down with Buck. Judge in the trial rips the increasingly unhinged prosecutor for criticizing Rittenhouse for exercising his right to remain silent. We may get a mistrial in Kenosha, despite the liberal media's demonization of someone based on nothing but hate.
